trans-unit.source: Defines a rectangular brush with a hatch style, a foreground color, and a background color.
trans-unit.target: Definerer et rektangulært velgeren med en skraveringsstilen, en forgrunnsfarge som og en bakgrunnsfarge.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: A hatch pattern is made from two colors: one defined by the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.BackgroundColor%2A>, which fills the background and one for the lines that form the pattern over the background defined by the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.ForegroundColor%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Et skraveringsmønster gjøres fra to farger: én definert av den <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.BackgroundColor%2A>, som fyller bakgrunnen og én for linjene som utgjør mønsteret over bakgrunnen som er definert av den <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.ForegroundColor%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.ForegroundColor%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.BackgroundColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.HatchStyle%2A> property defines what type of pattern the brush has and can be any value from the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.HatchStyle%2A>definerer hvilken type mønsteret i velgeren er og kan være en verdi fra den <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle>opplisting.</xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle> </xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchBrush.HatchStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: There are more than fifty elements in the <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Det finnes mer enn&50; elementer i den <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle>opplisting.</xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.HatchStyle>

trans-unit.source: The background color is initialized to black.
